5:
...This place is in shambles. Watch
your step, guys.
8:
This place is more rubble than ruins.
Razelt, are we in the correct location?
13:
We should be... These ruins have
been sleeping undisturbed for a
long time.
16:
I learned a little of Mosnian history
during the course of my extensive
education.
18:
In the far past, the Farlands and
Mosnia were engaged in a series of
skirmishes over territory.
22:
So, uh... Mosnia lost to the Farlands?
Is that what happened to them?
26:
No, the conflict never escalated into
war. There was no love lost between
our countries, but Mosnia fell to ruin
on its own.
28:
The cause was apparently civil war,
but I'm afraid I don't know the details.
32: A civil war, huh... What a way to go...
38:
Hey, isn't that the ruins of a gate?
Doesn't the shape look like the coat
of arms in your letters?
46:
Then I guess the Mosnia I knew was
never real.
54:
When I was little, Grey told me I was
a princess.
56:
So I started writing letters, hoping to
find my Prince Charming... And one
day, wouldn't you know it, a prince
started writing back.
60:
Isn't that just the strangest thing?
Letters from a prince of a country
that doesn't exist anymore!
69:
Hey, what're you looking sad for? I'm
totally fine!
72:
No matter who my prince was, he
was still my pen pal.
76: Plus now I've got friends like you!
83:
I'd be proud to call you a friend,
Prika!
88:
I as well. No matter what happens,
we will be there for you.
90:
Speaking of which... What do you
wish to do from here on out?
99:
That Simon guy said a whole bunch
of stuff that really made me mad.
102:
Do you think he's still waiting back
where we left him?
107:
He didn't follow us, so it's highly likely
that he remained there.
112:
Then I want to talk to him one more
time!
117:
Far be it for me to turn away a friend
in need! Be honored, for I shall
accompany you to see this dreadful
plight through!
130:
...Are you sure? I'm probably going to
drag you guys into another mess.
134:
I'm afraid that statement only
strengthens our resolve. Friends look
out for one another.
143:
Don't forget we still have to find Grey
too!
150:
Let's go pay Simon a visit then! Time
to get us some answers!
153:
Yeah... Yesterday was rough, but we
made it through somehow!
157:
We'll be okay no matter what
happens! Let's do this!
